  <text>
	Rings can be used in the manual crafring of 
    <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:materials/rotor" underlined="true">Rotors</style>,
	the creation of 
    <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:items/empty_cell" underlined="true">Cells</style>, and in the case of 
	the various rubber rings for making 
    <style color="0xbbffaa">Pumps</style> or steel and nickel zinc ferrite rings for making 
	
    <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:circuits/components" underlined="true">Inductors</style>.
  </text>
  <h3>Crafting</h3>
